{
  "stem": "4284.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, up to 1936, you were still able to use public transportation with some degree of safety because you weren't recognized to be Jewish.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before we had to wear the star, there was no distinction.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was rather on a regular basis, once or twice a year, to go and visit my grandparents, or my grandmother, in one case, yes.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The problems of 1938, of course, caused a rapid worsening of Jewish life in-- in Germany, especially in Cologne, Cologne having been a interesting city culturally and many other ways, and also strategically located near the French border.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's certainly very close to it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And also, it was a city that ultimately, with respect to World War II, became more strategic because it was a railroad facility that led into the countries that had been invaded, like Belgium and Holland.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1938, it became totally impossible to have any kind of a normal life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, for a 10-year-old that was puzzling. and you were quite confused as to the events to come.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All you know, you were terribly intimidated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, you really didn't leave the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And most important of all, the house we lived in, we had to vacate, which was actually an apartment, I should say.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We happened to be fortunate enough that my parents and I found a-- one room, with a tiny kitchen, in a Jewish-owned house, apartment house, which we did share with Gentiles.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, because it was a free-for-all against the Jews since 1938, the Gentiles in that house were not too kind to any coexistence with Jews in the same-- it was absolutely unpatriotic.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was-- you know, you were an absolute enemy.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
